    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. It runs smoothly, the interior is nice and comfy, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a solid, dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to have a blast driving it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
