      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Come by and see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 32500.0,
