      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a meticulously maintained example of the iconic S54 platform. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS, the powertrain delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory M-variable differential lock. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is robust, with recent valve adjustments and rod bearing service already addressed. A true driver\u2019s specification for those valuing mechanical purity and analog feedback.",
